enumerations.name: PduCollectionTriggerEnum
enumerations.note: Defines whether a Pdu contributes to the triggering of the data transmission if Pdu collection is enabled. Aggregated by ContainedIPduProps.trigger, IEEE1722TpAcfBusPart.collectionTrigger, SocketConnectionIpdu Identifier.pduCollectionTrigger, SoConIPduIdentifier.pduCollectionTrigger

literals.name: always
literals.description:
Pdu will trigger the transmission of the data.

literals.name: never
literals.description:
Pdu will be buffered and will not trigger the transmission of the data.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1
